                        會計與法律完美融合，<br />
                        構築企業永續的<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-accent to-brand-muted">雙重防護網</span>。
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-light/75 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl font-medium">
